    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "content": "Lily observes a splendid green apple. It rests here with a tiny brown stem, displaying its juicy form. This perfect specimen reminds us that we are counting one wonderful piece of fruit alone. We see the number one brightly displayed.",
      "source_page_number": 1,
