      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "content": "Next, we see two apples balanced carefully on the scale. One is bright pink, and the other vibrant red. This shows that we have successfully counted a total of two pieces of fruit.",
      "source_page_number": 2,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_002.jpg",
        "filename": "page_002.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
