      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "content": "Now, watch as one large green apple balances against two smaller ones: a red and a pink. We count them all togetherone big, two littlewhich means we have reached three apples! That is how addition works.",
      "source_page_number": 3,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_003.jpg",
        "filename": "page_003.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_5/page_003.mp3",
