        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "content": "Uh oh, the seesaw illustrates an imbalance of weight. The large green apple pulls down dramatically on one side. This shows us that bigger objects exert more force and are harder to lift!",
      "source_page_number": 4,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_004.jpg",
        "filename": "page_004.jpg",
