        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "However, two smaller apples are shown resting equally on the plank. They balance perfectly, creating a cheerful image. These small apples bring such happiness; they prove simple things can make us feel joy.",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
